title: Kellie Hindsley, 45, Frankfort, Indiana
content:
.

Kellie was a resident of Frankfort, Indiana at the time of her passing.

Kellie was a 1988 graduate of Frankfort High School.







Visitation and ServicesVisitation will be 3-8 p.m. Wednesday September 23 2015 at Goodwin Funeral Home. Services will be 11 a.m. Thursday September 24th at the funeral home. Burial will be in Green Lawn Memorial Park.
